data.description: This beautifully-updated Oviedo townhome features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, LOFT/BONUS SPACE  on the second floor, and an OFFICE on the first floor.  The main living space features NEW LAMINATE WOOD FLOORING, FRESH INTERIOR PAINT, and an OPEN FLOOR PLAN. Other appealing characteristics include new crown moulding, updated baseboards, high ceilings, recessed lighting, and display shelving.  The kitchen features CORIAN COUNTERTOPS, 36â CABINETS, NEW TILE BACKSPLASH, a BREAKFAST BAR, closet pantry, and oversized double sink.  Upstairs, you will find ALL NEW CARPET, a SPLIT FLOOR PLAN, and the conveniently-located laundry room. The loft is the perfect space for a media room, play room, or desk space.  The master suite features a WALKIN CLOSET, DUAL SINK with ample counterspace, GARDEN TUB, and WALKIN TILE SHOWER.  You have multiple options from which to enjoy the beautiful Florida weather.  The front of the home features an open paver patio with space for a bistro set.  There is a SCREENED PATIO at the rear of the home, perfect for grilling and entertaining.  This property has NO REAR NEIGHBORS!  The Seminole Trail runs behind the community, giving you a great opportunity to bike, walk, or picnic.  This is a GATED COMMUNITY. There are numerous shopping and dining options just minutes from the property.  It also provides easy access to the 417 expressway, leading to easy access to multiple airports and theme parks/resorts. Aloma/426 offers direct access to Winter Park's Rollins College and Park Avenue.
data.whatILove: Great location on the Cross-Seminole trail. Very quiet small community.
